## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c5b30-102">O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> objeto tem um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> propriedade que pode ser atribuída a uma execução longa <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> no manipulador para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5b30-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object has a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property that can be assigned to a long-running <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> in the handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceView.ContextCreating> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c5b30-103">Para obter mais informações, consulte [o gerenciamento de ciclo de vida de contexto de objeto (EntityDataSource)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5b30-103">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c5b30-104">O exemplo a seguir mostra a criação de um <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variável do <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> objeto e sua atribuição para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> propriedade do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> objeto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c5b30-104">The following example shows the creation of an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and its assignment to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>  
  
```  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)  
        {  
            e.Context = objCtx;  
        }  
    }  
  
```

  
  
